  "texts": [
    "In assessing the performance across various models on MOSI, our MMER-TD (Ours) model has demonstrated significant advantages in multiple metrics.",
    "Specifically, it achieved 83.53 % in binary accuracy and 83.41 % in F1 Score, surpassing other models.",
    "Furthermore, it exhibited commendable performance in Mean Absolute Error, recording a score of 71.710, indicative of high predictive precision.",
    "The model also scored the highest in correlation at 79.210, suggesting a strong agreement with the true outcomes.",
    "In the more stringent multi-class accuracy tests, our model attained high scores of 52.190 % and 45.480 %, respectively."
  ],
